com.communote.plugins.core.views.annotations

Annotation Type Page


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Page
    Annotation for providing additional information to the page. The controller must be of type ViewController.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String menu
      Key for the menu, this page is for.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String[] cssCategories
      List of names of the categories which group the CSS resources that should be included when rendering the page.
      String[] jsCategories
      List of names of the categories which group the JavaScript resources that should be included when rendering the page.
      String jsMessagesCategory
      The category for which the localized JavaScript messages should be included
      String menuMessageKey
      Defines the message key to be used for menu entries directing to this page.
      String submenu
      Key for the submenu, this page is on
      String titleKey
      Message key for the title to be shown on the page.

    • Element Detail

      • menu

        public abstract String menu
        Key for the menu, this page is for.

      • cssCategories

        public abstract String[] cssCategories
        List of names of the categories which group the CSS resources that should be included when rendering the page. The categories are included in order.
        Default:
        {}

      • jsCategories

        public abstract String[] jsCategories
        List of names of the categories which group the JavaScript resources that should be included when rendering the page. The categories are included in order.
        Default:
        {}

      • jsMessagesCategory

        public abstract String jsMessagesCategory
        The category for which the localized JavaScript messages should be included
        Default:
        ""

      • menuMessageKey

        public abstract String menuMessageKey
        Defines the message key to be used for menu entries directing to this page.
        Default:
        ""

      • submenu

        public abstract String submenu
        Key for the submenu, this page is on
        Default:
        ""

      • titleKey

        public abstract String titleKey
        Message key for the title to be shown on the page. The message can have a place holder which will be passed the name of the current client. The ViewController will for example expose the message under the variable pageTitle.
        Default:
        ""
